\v 35 Labantu bema babukela\x + Hlab. 22.17.\x*. Lababusi kanye labo\x + Mat. 27.41,42. Mark. 15.31. Joha. 3.1.\x* ba\add m\add*klolodela, besithi: Wasindisa abanye, kazisindise yena, uba yena enguKristu\x + 16.14.\x*, okhethiweyo kaNkulunkulu\x + Isa. 28.16. Mat. 24.22.\x*.
