\v 39 Lomunye wabenzi bobubi ababelengisiwe\x + Mat. 27.44. Mark. 15.32.\x* wamthuka\x + 22.65.\x*, esithi: Uba wena unguKristu, zisindise wena lathi\x + 23.35.\x*.
\v 40 Kodwa omunye waphendula emkhuza, esithi: Wena kawumesabi yini uNkulunkulu, lokhu lawe ukulokhukulahlwa?
