\v 50 Njalo khangela, indoda ethiwa nguJosefa\x + Mat. 27.57-61. Mark. 15.42-47. Joha. 19.38-42.\x*, ilunga lomphakathi\x + Mark. 15.43.\x*, indoda elungileyo eqotho\x + Seb. 11.24.\x*;
\v 51 yena wayengavumelananga lecebo lesenzo sabo; \add waye\add*vela eArimathiya umuzi wamaJuda, laye ngokwakhe\x + Mark. 15.43.\x* wayelindele umbuso kaNkulunkulu\x + 2.25,38.\x*;
