\v 54 Kwakulusuku lwamalungiselelo, lesabatha\x + Mat. 27.62.\x* laselisondela\x + Mat. 28.1.\x*.
\v 55 Labesifazana, ababeze laye bevela eGalili\x + 8.2.\x*, balandela, balibona ingcwaba, lokuthi isidumbu sibekwe njani\x + Mark. 15.47.\x*.
\v 56 Basebebuyela emuva balungisa amakha lamagcobo\x + Mark. 16.1. Luka 24.1. Joha. 19.39.\x*. Ngesabatha basebephumula njengokomlayo\x + Eks. 20.10.\x*.